casebody.data:
Argued and submitted December 20, 1991, judicial review dismissed February 12, JEFFERY LYNN HODGES, Petitioner, v. BOARD OF PAROLE, Respondent. (CA A66125) 823 P2d 1051 Lawrence J. Hall, Deputy Public Defender, Salem, argued the cause for petitioner. With him on the brief was Sally L. Avera, Public Defender, Salem. Yuanxing Chen, Assistant Attorney General, Salem, argued the cause for respondent. With him on the brief were Dave Frohnmayer, Attorney General, and Virginia L. Linder, Solicitor General, Salem. PER CURIAM

decision withdrawn on court’s own motion by order dated September 9, 1992

Before Warren, Presiding Judge, and Riggs and Edmonds, Judges.
